      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must pass manufactured-solution or benchmark verification tests confirming correct implementation of governing equations.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver confirms second-order spatial convergence. Benchmark against lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step yields results within 1% of published reference data."
