      "rationale": "Validation activities used the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry—identical to the COU device family—operated across the full CPB flow-speed envelope. Blood analog fluid properties match within physiological range. Geometric similarity between validation and COU configurations confirmed by overlay comparison."
    },
