      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; sample representativeness addressed through operating-point selection.",
      "rationale": "Formal statistical characterization of test sample variability not required at MRL 2. Five operating points selected to span the clinical CPB envelope (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM) based on clinical use data from the device IFU. Coverage of worst-case conditions confirmed by operating-point analysis."
    },
