      "rationale": "Quantitative equivalency assessment of input parameters between validation and COU configurations not required at MRL 2. Qualitative review confirms fluid properties, geometric scale, and operating range are equivalent between the validation platform and the COU. No significant parameter mismatch identified that would invalidate the credibility argument."
